We saw what you said.  I understand where you are coming from, but I do not think you understand why some people would do this.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  Had they been sincere about their emotion, why not log off EQ and go to earn some extra bucks for donation. <br>
<br>
